  "detailed_description": "'Jesus Christ Simulator' is a new take on the 'Superhero Simulator' game genre.<br>The game immerses you in a huge American City, where you are tasked by God with fixing the broken system that humans have been forced to live in.<br><br>You are 'the' Ultimate Superhero!<br><br>You will help bring prosperity to humankind, and use your Powers to bring light back to the world.<br><br>Perform exorcisms, pay off people's debts, pay their rent, furnish them with a car, and much more... You will do the things that actual superheroes would do!<br><br>As Jesus, you can travel to Hell and save the souls that are trapped there, from their torment! Or condemn them for their crimes!<br><br>Armed with Unlimited Miracles, Flight, God Lasers, and Superpowers, you can use your power to change the world, to help people, to save lives, and to destroy the system that enslaves them!<br><br>But beware, there are demons everywhere...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921650/extras/4334f655c4ad727ea7e42e57da4edb43.poster.avif?t=1773366084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921650/extras/4334f655c4ad727ea7e42e57da4edb43.webm?t=1773366084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921650/extras/4334f655c4ad727ea7e42e57da4edb43.mp4?t=1773366084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921650/extras/d51846d567c0c641cc1dbe2403e20952.poster.avif?t=1773366084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921650/extras/d51846d567c0c641cc1dbe2403e20952.webm?t=1773366084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921650/extras/d51846d567c0c641cc1dbe2403e20952.mp4?t=1773366084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921650/extras/ab183121999977e81442bce0fc34b141.poster.avif?t=1773366084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921650/extras/ab183121999977e81442bce0fc34b141.webm?t=1773366084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921650/extras/ab183121999977e81442bce0fc34b141.mp4?t=1773366084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921650/extras/71bbf3425783d99839a0bc789dd236c9.poster.avif?t=1773366084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921650/extras/71bbf3425783d99839a0bc789dd236c9.webm?t=1773366084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921650/extras/71bbf3425783d99839a0bc789dd236c9.mp4?t=1773366084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>More playable cities are being planned for the future!!!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921650/extras/951aac3a18226adbdf0a3d6be662186b.poster.avif?t=1773366084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921650/extras/951aac3a18226adbdf0a3d6be662186b.webm?t=1773366084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.